Frequently Asked Questions

Everything you need to know about our pricing and services.

How do you calculate pricing?

Our pricing is based on factors like distance, service type, time requirements, and any special handling needs. We provide transparent quotes with no hidden fees.

Are there any additional fees?

No hidden fees! Our quotes include all standard services. Additional charges may apply for special requests or services outside normal business hours.

Do you offer discounts?

Yes! We offer discounts for recurring customers, bulk services, and seasonal promotions. Check our current offers when requesting a quote.

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept cash, credit cards, debit cards, and digital payment methods. Payment is typically due upon completion of service.
